title: NOFX - Backstage Passport Ep. 2 .MPG
description: This episode focuses mostly on the Peru disaster. It briefly discusses a gig in Ecuador on tennis courts, but most of the show is about Peru where the gig was to be played in an area that "closely resembles that lake they played at in 1987" according to the Peruvian promoter. The crew gets into a bad situation while the band is dining on fancy food, and to avoid a riot Fat Mike gives an impromptu acoustic performance
